Also, given the large amounts of activity of both the Bloodsabers and the Temple of Life lately, I would consider the Plane of Health as a possible upcoming plane.  This would give the oft-neglected Qeynos paladins something to be happy about.<br>
In short, instead of griping about ND, it would probably make sense for paladins (or at least those who would be affected by the aforementioned planes) to push for the inclusion of the new planes.  Then if VI decides not to institute an ND item for those paladins, make a fuss about it until something is instituted.<br>
